ms\". In 1995 he was awarded the Prix\nAlbert-Tessier.\n","linknr":155,"url":"Jean-Pierre_Lefebvre","recorded":1375082955,"links":["/w/index.php?title=Jean_Pierre_Lefebvre&action=edit","/w/index.php?title=Jean_Pierre_Lefebvre&action=edit","//bits.wikimedia.org/favicon/wikipedia.ico","/w/opensearch_desc.php","//en.wikipedia.org/w/api.php?action=rsd","//creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/","/w/index.php?title=Special:RecentChanges&feed=atom","/wiki/Jean_Pierre_Lefebvre","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=ext.gadget.DRN-wizard%2CReferenceTooltips%2Ccharinsert%2Cteahouse%7Cext.rtlcite%2Cwikihiero%7Cext.uls.nojs%7Cmediawiki.legacy.commonPrint%2Cshared%7Cmw.PopUpMediaTransform%7Cskins.vector&only=styles&skin=vector&*","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=site&only=styles&skin=vector&*","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=startup&only=scripts&skin=vector&*","//bits.wikimedia.org/geoiplookup","//meta.wikimedia.org","/w/index.php?title=Jean-Pierre_Lefebvre&redirect=no","#mw-navigation","#p-search","/wiki/Montreal","/wiki/Canada","/wiki/Film_director","/wiki/Screenwriter","/wiki/1965_in_film","/wiki/French_Canadian","#cite_note-1","//fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mon_amie_Pierrette","/wiki/Ra%C3%B4ul_Duguay","/wiki/Cl%C3%A9ment_Perron","#cite_note-pierrette-2","#cite_note-cfe-3","/wiki/Cannes_Film_Festival","#cite_note-cfe-3","/wiki/Le_jour_S...","/wiki/Un_Certain_Regard","#cite_note-4","/w/index.php?title=Marcel_Sabourin&action=edit&redlink=1","/wiki/Order_of_Canada","#cite_note-5","/wiki/Prix_Albert-Tessier","#Filmography","#Features","#Other_Work","#References","#External_links","/w/index.php?title=Jean_Pierre_Lefebvre&action=edit&section=1","/w/index.php?title=Jean_Pierre_Lefebvre&action=edit&section=2","/wiki/Le_jour_S...","/w/index.php?title=Jean_Pierre_Lefebvre&action=edit&section=3","/w/index.php?title=Jean_Pierre_Lefebvre&action=edit&section=4","#cite_r